Duet Webcam Bridge bundles a prebuilt static build of FFmpeg in its release
archives for convenience. FFmpeg is a separate work with its own license and is
not covered by this project's MIT license.

FFmpeg: https://ffmpeg.org/  (licensed under the GPL/LGPL)

The bundled binaries come from these upstream static-build providers, which also
publish the corresponding source code:
  - Windows: https://www.gyan.dev/ffmpeg/builds/
  - Linux (incl. Raspberry Pi): https://johnvansickle.com/ffmpeg/
  - macOS:   https://evermeet.cx/ffmpeg/

If you redistribute a release archive, you must comply with FFmpeg's license
terms, including making the corresponding FFmpeg source available (the links
above satisfy this for the bundled builds).
